  dialogNodes:
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'The Knight stares blankly at you.


      What do you want?'
    nextOption: Where are the bunnies?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: What bunnies?
    nextOption: I need your help saving the world
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: What do bunnies have to do with that?
    nextOption: I must defeat the bunnies to save the world
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: '[Rolls his eyes and mutters something under his breath about crazy
      peasants]


      I think those zombies over there already saved the world
      for you.


      They slaughtered all the bunnies!'
    nextOption: Zombies?  Aaaaah
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'The dead have come back to life and trapped us in here.


      If
      we can''t defeat them we won''t even survive the night.'
    nextOption: That does sound serious
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 10
    description: 'If you want the help of the SunSworn, you must prove yourself to
      the High Priestess.


      Join our ranks and help us fight these undead.


      If
      we survive, the Priestess will be in your debt and will help you with anything
      you need.'
    nextOption: Deal!
